{
  "texts": [
    "AI technology, like chatbots and virtual assistants, allows organizations to customize products, services, and marketing to customer preferences.",
    "This boosts consumer satisfaction, engagement, and corporate performance.",
    "Examples in e-commerce, retail, travel and hospitality, financial services, and healthcare show that AI-powered",
    "AI-driven customization has transformed how companies customize products for customers.",
    "AI algorithms allow organizations to collect and analyze massive volumes of client data to understand their preferences, purchasing history, and behavior."
  ]
}